comment._content: Compare with www.flickr.com/photos/anmm_thecommons/7264639598/ This pic appears to have been taken pre 1893 floods...my guess is ca. 1890-91...in this pic we see the City Tabernacle Baptist Church...which was evidently built in the period 1889-1891 (it's unclear whether we see the finished product above) nla.gov.au/nla.news-article20721858 ...note also the Ship Inn, in Stanley St...the 1893 flood pic shows it with a significant addition...
